rows.label: tlk46400079_02_msg0001
rows.name:
With the summit over, the emergency
security measures have been lifted.

rows.label: tlk46400079_02_msg0002
rows.name:
However, I feel there is still tension
hanging in the air of the city.

rows.label: tlk46400079_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Even the holy songs that ring out
through the plaza sound somehow
strained to my ears today.
